        <article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-4">Fart&#xF8;y med adgang til &#xE5; delta kan fiske f&#xF8;lgende kvanta torsk (tonn): <table><thead><tr><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Hjemmelslengde</i></th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Kvotefaktor</i></th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Garantert kvote<br/>st&#xF8;rste lengde under 11 m</i></th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Maksimalkvote<br/>St&#xF8;rste lengde under 11 m</i></th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Garantert kvote<br/>St&#xF8;rste lengde over 11 m</i></th><th data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top"><i>Maksimalkvote<br/>St&#xF8;rste lengde over 11 m</i></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">Under 7 meter</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">1,21</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">42,5</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">70,8</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">35,4</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">49,6</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">7&#x2013;7,9</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">1,43</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">50,2</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">83,7</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">41,8</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">58,6</td></tr><tr><td data-text-align="center" data-vertical-align="top">8&#x2013;8,9</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">1,70</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">59,7</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">99,5</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">49,7</td><td data-text-align="right" data-vertical-align="top">69,6</td></tr><tr><td data